@startuml
'Test transform on groups - all children should inherit group transform
skinparam backgroundColor white
sprite $groupTest <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100" width="100" height="100">
  <g transform="translate(30, 30)">
    <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="8" fill="blue"/>
    <rect x="5" y="25" width="10" height="10" fill="green"/>
  </g>
  <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="8" fill="red" fill-opacity="0.3"/>
  <rect x="5" y="25" width="10" height="10" fill="orange" fill-opacity="0.3"/>
</svg>

title Transform Group Test
:The blue circle and green square are in a translated group;
:They should appear shifted 30 units right and down;
:Red circle and orange square are untransformed references;
:<$groupTest>;
@enduml
